11
00:02:14,920 --> 00:02:19,120
Happy birthday, Li Weihao.

12
00:02:20,520 --> 00:02:22,720
Excuse me, you dropped your student ID.

13
00:02:28,000 --> 00:02:29,120
Is anyone there?

14
00:02:29,600 --> 00:02:30,320
Help!

15
00:02:33,000 --> 00:02:34,640
Your mother's and my lives

16
00:02:35,360 --> 00:02:36,960
