17
00:02:50,440 --> 00:02:50,920
Chao,

18
00:02:51,880 --> 00:02:52,960
are you still busy?

19
00:02:53,200 --> 00:02:53,840
Well,

20
00:02:53,840 --> 00:02:54,640
the money,

21
00:02:54,640 --> 00:02:56,200
I've already transferred it to your account.

22
00:02:56,200 --> 00:02:56,920
In addition,

23
00:02:56,920 --> 00:02:58,520
I added 500 yuan for you.

24
00:02:58,880 --> 00:02:59,940
Eat and drink well.

25
00:03:00,440 --> 00:03:02,500
Call me anytime if you need anything.

26
00:03:02,520 --> 00:03:04,120
I don't want the extra money.

27
00:03:06,480 --> 00:03:08,240
Be nicer to Qiong University students from now on.

28
00:03:08,240 --> 00:03:08,640
Okay.

29
00:03:08,640 --> 00:03:09,560
No problem.

30
00:03:09,560 --> 00:03:10,920
When Qiong University students come in the future,

31
00:03:10,920 --> 00:03:12,450
they all get a 20% discount.

32
00:03:13,200 --> 00:03:13,760
Okay.

33
00:03:13,760 --> 00:03:14,960
Then you carry on.

34
00:03:15,280 --> 00:03:16,010
Don't worry.

35
00:03:17,760 --> 00:03:18,420
Zhang Chao,

36
00:03:20,320 --> 00:03:20,960
let's go.

37
00:03:21,880 --> 00:03:23,480
How much longer do you think

38
00:03:23,480 --> 00:03:24,760
it will take?

39
00:03:29,360 --> 00:03:31,640
There's no time left.

40
00:03:31,640 --> 00:03:33,300
What do you mean, no time left?

41
00:03:34,040 --> 00:03:35,079
What's going on?

42
00:03:35,079 --> 00:03:35,720
Chao.

43
00:03:36,320 --> 00:03:37,079
Chao.

44
00:03:37,079 --> 00:03:38,210
What's wrong, Chao?

45
00:03:48,360 --> 00:03:49,120
Li Weihao.

46
00:03:50,280 --> 00:03:51,120
Li Weihao.

47
00:05:08,440 --> 00:05:10,000
Did you put salt in my food again just now?

48
00:05:10,000 --> 00:05:11,080
No, I didn't put anything in it.

49
00:05:11,080 --> 00:05:12,920
You didn't? Why is it so salty then?

50
00:05:12,920 --> 00:05:13,850
You put too much.

51
00:05:23,400 --> 00:05:24,400
Sami.

52
00:05:24,400 --> 00:05:25,160
Xiaoyu.

53
00:05:25,160 --> 00:05:26,960
Li Weihao jumped off a building.

54
00:05:27,640 --> 00:05:29,120
Jumped off a building.

55
00:05:29,840 --> 00:05:30,560
That's good.

56
00:05:30,560 --> 00:05:32,159
I'm still too busy right now.

57
00:05:32,440 --> 00:05:33,560
Thank you.

58
00:05:33,920 --> 00:05:35,520
Come on, thank you everyone.

59
00:05:36,920 --> 00:05:37,640
Uncle, Auntie.

60
00:05:37,640 --> 00:05:39,080
I'll go take a call first.

61
00:05:39,080 --> 00:05:39,880
Excuse me.

62
00:05:41,640 --> 00:05:42,920
Come on, let's have another toast.

63
00:05:42,920 --> 00:05:44,720
Alright, cheers.

64
00:05:44,720 --> 00:05:45,580
Hello, Mr. Lin.

65
00:05:46,680 --> 00:05:48,280
Li Weihao jumped off a building.

66
00:05:48,280 --> 00:05:49,120
Are you crazy?

67
00:05:49,480 --> 00:05:50,960
Really? You didn't know?

68
00:06:05,920 --> 00:06:06,520
What?

69
00:06:09,880 --> 00:06:11,360
Coward.

70
00:06:11,920 --> 00:06:12,850
What did you say?

71
00:06:13,800 --> 00:06:14,640
Nothing.

72
00:06:14,640 --> 00:06:16,120
A student at school

73
00:06:16,600 --> 00:06:17,720
took things too hard

74
00:06:17,720 --> 00:06:18,380
and is gone.

75
00:06:18,960 --> 00:06:19,800
What?

76
00:06:20,520 --> 00:06:22,480
What do you mean, gone?

77
00:06:24,160 --> 00:06:25,880
Stop talking nonsense!

78
00:06:25,880 --> 00:06:27,880
My son had dinner at home tonight.

79
00:06:27,880 --> 00:06:28,520
Let me tell you,

80
00:06:28,520 --> 00:06:31,580
cursing someone will bring death to your whole family.

81
00:06:31,880 --> 00:06:32,810
What's going on?

82
00:06:32,920 --> 00:06:34,080
A scam call.

83
00:06:34,440 --> 00:06:36,000
I'm so angry.

84
00:06:37,040 --> 00:06:38,370
Do you know what he said?

85
00:06:38,600 --> 00:06:39,720
He said our son...

86
00:06:42,080 --> 00:06:43,720
I can't say it.

87
00:06:43,720 --> 00:06:44,840
It's too unlucky.

88
00:06:45,440 --> 00:06:46,280
Enough.

89
00:06:46,480 --> 00:06:47,760
My heart is pounding.

90
00:06:47,760 --> 00:06:49,020
It's going to jump out.

91
00:06:49,640 --> 00:06:51,760
I was almost angered to death.

92
00:06:51,760 --> 00:06:53,120
What's wrong?

93
00:06:54,560 --> 00:06:55,480
This child.

94
00:06:58,200 --> 00:06:59,920
It's this scam call again.

95
00:07:00,640 --> 00:07:03,080
Is it that serious? It's just a scam call.

96
00:07:03,080 --> 00:07:04,160
You're so scared. I'll answer it.

97
00:07:04,160 --> 00:07:05,520
So infuriating.

98
00:07:08,120 --> 00:07:09,200
Hello, who is it?

99
00:07:09,800 --> 00:07:10,930
Give him a scolding.

100
00:07:19,240 --> 00:07:20,200
What happened?

101
00:07:20,720 --> 00:07:21,480
Let's go.

102
00:07:21,480 --> 00:07:22,920
Where are we going?

103
00:07:24,040 --> 00:07:24,840
The morgue.

104
00:07:37,360 --> 00:07:38,000
Another round.

105
00:07:38,000 --> 00:07:39,000
Alright, cheers.

106
00:08:25,280 --> 00:08:27,010
Why are you staying here alone?

107
00:08:27,680 --> 00:08:29,940
I'm not interested in this kind of event.

108
00:08:30,320 --> 00:08:31,400
Me neither.

109
00:08:33,440 --> 00:08:34,880
I have big news.

110
00:08:34,880 --> 00:08:36,080
Do you want to hear it?

111
00:08:36,159 --> 00:08:37,320
No.

112
00:08:37,320 --> 00:08:38,679
Don't try to get close to me.

113
00:08:38,679 --> 00:08:40,539
I'm not interested in you either.

114
00:08:42,240 --> 00:08:44,560
Someone jumped off a building at Qiong University.

115
00:08:44,560 --> 00:08:45,690
You should know him.

116
00:08:46,680 --> 00:08:47,880
His name is Li Weihao.

117
00:08:49,240 --> 00:08:49,920
What?

118
00:09:08,480 --> 00:09:11,280
Xiaochao, you are my best friend.

119
00:09:11,280 --> 00:09:13,520
Xiaohao, you too. Come and catch me.

120
00:09:13,520 --> 00:09:14,580
You can't catch me.

121
00:09:15,720 --> 00:09:17,240
I will catch you soon.

122
00:09:17,240 --> 00:09:18,520
Come and catch me.

123
00:09:19,000 --> 00:09:20,400
You can't catch me, Xiaohao.

124
00:09:20,400 --> 00:09:21,560
Wait for me.

125
00:09:38,560 --> 00:09:39,600
Li Weihao.

126
00:09:44,280 --> 00:09:45,320
I'm sorry, Chao.

127
00:09:45,840 --> 00:09:47,300
I didn't turn off my alarm.

128
00:09:53,080 --> 00:09:54,280
Li Weihao is gone.

129
00:09:56,440 --> 00:09:57,560
He's dead.

130
00:10:00,240 --> 00:10:01,400
Chao.

131
00:10:01,400 --> 00:10:02,800
Are you okay, Chao?

132
00:10:17,600 --> 00:10:18,360
Chao.

133
00:10:19,000 --> 00:10:20,360
What's wrong, Chao?

134
00:10:22,080 --> 00:10:23,760
Are you really okay, Chao?

135
00:10:24,360 --> 00:10:24,880
Chao.

136
00:10:26,960 --> 00:10:27,720
Chao.

137
00:10:27,720 --> 00:10:29,320
What's wrong with you, Chao?

138
00:10:29,960 --> 00:10:30,560
Chao.

139
00:10:30,560 --> 00:10:31,640
Look at me, Chao.

140
00:10:31,640 --> 00:10:32,440
Chao.

141
00:10:32,840 --> 00:10:33,480
Chao.

142
00:10:34,080 --> 00:10:35,080
Let me help you up.

143
00:10:38,160 --> 00:10:39,760
Let me take you to the infirmary.

144
00:10:39,760 --> 00:10:40,760
I'm fine.

145
00:10:42,360 --> 00:10:43,640
I'm going out for some fresh air. Slow down.

146
00:10:43,640 --> 00:10:44,440
I'm fine.

147
00:11:10,120 --> 00:11:10,680
Who is it?

148
00:11:12,680 --> 00:11:13,480
Who?

149
00:11:15,360 --> 00:11:16,040
Who is it?

150
00:11:20,880 --> 00:11:21,920
Stop right there.

151
00:11:29,480 --> 00:11:30,440
Stop.

152
00:11:42,560 --> 00:11:43,520
Come on.

153
00:11:47,960 --> 00:11:49,600
Come on.

154
00:12:41,920 --> 00:12:42,720
Who is it?

155
00:12:58,560 --> 00:12:59,360
Who?

156
00:13:24,600 --> 00:13:25,280
Wu Yu.

157
00:13:29,040 --> 00:13:29,880
Are you out of your mind?

158
00:13:29,880 --> 00:13:30,800
Are you crazy?

159
00:13:30,800 --> 00:13:32,120
Scaring people in the middle of the night.

160
00:13:32,120 --> 00:13:33,560
I just came downstairs.

161
00:13:33,560 --> 00:13:34,640
How did I scare you?

162
00:13:34,640 --> 00:13:35,640
Stop pretending.

163
00:13:35,840 --> 00:13:36,900
Step back a little.

164
00:13:38,640 --> 00:13:40,120
Didn't you just go to the bathroom?

165
00:13:40,120 --> 00:13:40,840
No.

166
00:13:41,040 --> 00:13:41,840
I really didn't.

167
00:13:41,840 --> 00:13:42,920
I came downstairs.

168
00:13:42,920 --> 00:13:44,580
Why would I go to the bathroom?

169
00:13:49,920 --> 00:13:51,780
Did you see a dark shadow just now?

170
00:13:53,240 --> 00:13:54,400
Now that you mention it,

171
00:13:54,400 --> 00:13:55,160
