172
00:13:55,160 --> 00:13:56,080
I really saw a dark shadow

173
00:13:56,080 --> 00:13:57,920
flash by over there.

174
00:14:01,000 --> 00:14:02,120
Tell me,

175
00:14:02,120 --> 00:14:03,320
could that shadow

176
00:14:03,880 --> 00:14:05,840
be Weihao?

177
00:14:09,960 --> 00:14:11,290
Stop talking nonsense.

178
00:14:27,880 --> 00:14:28,880
Turn it off.

179
00:14:38,560 --> 00:14:39,620
What are you doing?

180
00:14:39,680 --> 00:14:40,640
I saw a shadow.

181
00:14:47,520 --> 00:14:48,180
Where is it?

182
00:14:50,000 --> 00:14:51,200
It was there just now.

183
00:14:54,760 --> 00:14:55,880
Are you crazy?

184
00:14:56,320 --> 00:14:57,040
No.

185
00:14:58,160 --> 00:14:59,520
I just saw a shadow.

186
00:15:00,000 --> 00:15:01,000
Is it Weihao?

187
00:15:02,720 --> 00:15:04,440
