202
00:16:09,280 --> 00:16:10,680
No? Come on, let me drive.

203
00:16:18,080 --> 00:16:18,680
Come on.

204
00:16:29,920 --> 00:16:30,680
Let's go.

205
00:16:30,680 --> 00:16:31,400
Hurry up.

206
00:16:58,880 --> 00:17:00,840
I'm going to the restroom.

207
00:17:01,400 --> 00:17:02,930
Nobody is allowed to leave.

208
00:17:03,080 --> 00:17:05,079
I'll be right back.

209
00:17:08,599 --> 00:17:09,839
I'll go with you, boss.

210
00:17:09,839 --> 00:17:10,599
Go back

211
00:17:11,160 --> 00:17:12,319
and keep an eye on them.

212
00:17:12,319 --> 00:17:13,119
Okay.

213
00:17:15,680 --> 00:17:16,960
My boss said

214
00:17:16,960 --> 00:17:18,680
nobody can leave.

215
00:17:46,320 --> 00:17:52,640
Beat you to death!

216
00:17:52,640 --> 00:17:53,680
Go to hell!

217
00:18:20,200 --> 00:18:22,120
No offense, Weihao.

218
00:18:22,120 --> 00:18:23,240
Have a good rest.

219
00:18:23,560 --> 00:18:24,560
Brother Chao.

220
00:18:25,800 --> 00:18:26,840
Brother Chao.

221
00:18:31,200 --> 00:18:32,640
Brother Chao.

222
00:18:33,400 --> 00:18:34,720
Do you feel

223
00:18:34,720 --> 00:18:36,480
that this room is a bit chilly?

224
00:18:37,040 --> 00:18:37,760
How about

225
00:18:37,760 --> 00:18:39,920
we squeeze into one bed tonight?

226
00:18:40,760 --> 00:18:41,600
Sure.

227
00:18:42,600 --> 00:18:43,560
Welcome.

228
00:18:44,920 --> 00:18:46,080
Great.

229
00:18:51,920 --> 00:18:52,880
Go away.

230
00:18:53,680 --> 00:18:55,080
Why are you in my bed?

231
00:18:56,240 --> 00:18:57,080
Chao.

232
00:18:58,600 --> 00:18:59,440
Last night,

233
00:18:59,440 --> 00:19:01,240
didn't I ask if we could sleep together?

234
00:19:01,240 --> 00:19:02,720
You agreed to it yourself.

235
00:19:02,720 --> 00:19:04,360
Take your pillow and get out.

236
00:19:04,360 --> 00:19:05,160
Chao.

237
00:19:05,960 --> 00:19:06,520
Chao.

238
00:19:06,840 --> 00:19:07,520
Chao, listen to me.

239
00:19:07,520 --> 00:19:08,920
You held my hand last night.

240
00:19:08,920 --> 00:19:09,680
Why are you... Let go!

241
00:19:09,680 --> 00:19:10,760
Let go.

242
00:19:12,480 --> 00:19:13,400
Fine, I'll go.

243
00:19:13,960 --> 00:19:15,320
You turn your back and deny everything.

244
00:19:15,320 --> 00:19:16,440
This is my pillow.

245
00:19:17,080 --> 00:19:17,920
Take it back.

246
00:19:41,680 --> 00:19:42,280
Thank you.

247
00:19:48,280 --> 00:19:49,320
Oh, my god.

248
00:19:49,320 --> 00:19:51,600
Is that Li Weihao from the Design Department?

249
00:19:51,600 --> 00:19:52,280
Poor thing.

250
00:19:52,280 --> 00:19:53,480
He was so young.

251
00:19:53,480 --> 00:19:55,010
Just passed away like this.

252
00:19:55,080 --> 00:19:55,920
Excuse me,

253
00:19:55,920 --> 00:19:56,560
hello.

254
00:19:57,480 --> 00:19:59,800
What did you say about Li Weihao?

255
00:19:59,800 --> 00:20:02,660
He jumped off the building last night. Right there.

256
00:20:50,600 --> 00:20:51,560
I have good news for you.

257
00:20:51,560 --> 00:20:53,490
We are getting married next month!

258
00:20:53,520 --> 00:20:54,440
Really?

259
00:20:54,440 --> 00:20:55,600
Come on, cheers!

260
00:20:58,800 --> 00:20:59,560
My bad, my bad.

261
00:20:59,560 --> 00:21:01,690
