262
00:21:01,920 --> 00:21:03,780
Here, I'll pour you a little more.

263
00:21:06,960 --> 00:21:08,690
Let's make big money together.

264
00:21:31,360 --> 00:21:33,090
I wish Mr. Chen happy every day!

265
00:21:37,760 --> 00:21:42,240
The number you dialed is powered off.

266
00:21:53,400 --> 00:21:54,360
Weihao,

267
00:21:54,360 --> 00:21:55,640
I will go to Qiongzhou tomorrow

268
00:21:55,640 --> 00:21:56,520
