269
00:22:01,080 --> 00:22:02,200
I'm sorry.

270
00:22:05,720 --> 00:22:07,400
I'm late.

271
00:22:10,560 --> 00:22:11,840
Let us in.

272
00:22:11,840 --> 00:22:13,160
We want to see the principal.

273
00:22:13,160 --> 00:22:15,820
What are you doing? We want to see the principal.

274
00:22:15,920 --> 00:22:16,880
Let us go.

275
00:22:16,880 --> 00:22:18,920
What are you doing? We want to see the principal.

276
00:22:18,920 --> 00:22:21,560
Let us in. Don't stop us.

277
00:22:21,560 --> 00:22:22,880
I have to go in. Let us in.

278
00:22:22,880 --> 00:22:24,160
Stop.

279
00:22:24,160 --> 00:22:25,040
Let me go.

280
00:22:25,840 --> 00:22:30,840
Give my son back!

281
00:22:30,840 --> 00:22:33,600
My son was fine when he arrived.

282
00:22:33,600 --> 00:22:35,840
How did he become like this?

283
00:22:35,840 --> 00:22:37,970
How does your school manage students?

284
00:22:39,000 --> 00:22:40,000
I'm sorry.

285
00:22:40,000 --> 00:22:41,440
It's our school's negligence

286
00:22:41,440 --> 00:22:42,600
