287
00:22:42,600 --> 00:22:44,040
Is "sorry" useful?

288
00:22:44,040 --> 00:22:46,240
Can it bring my son back to life?

289
00:22:46,680 --> 00:22:49,080
What's wrong with you?

290
00:22:51,800 --> 00:22:53,360
Give my son back! I can fully understand

291
00:22:53,360 --> 00:22:54,760
your feelings.

292
00:22:55,360 --> 00:22:56,640
If this punch

293
00:22:56,640 --> 00:22:58,080
can relieve your anger,

294
00:22:58,640 --> 00:23:00,040
I am willing to take a few more punches.

295
00:23:00,040 --> 00:23:01,920
It's a bargain for you to take a few punches.

296
00:23:01,920 --> 00:23:03,080
I'm telling you,

297
00:23:03,080 --> 00:23:05,440
you must hand over the murderer to me today.

298
00:23:05,440 --> 00:23:07,400
I want him to pay for my son's life.

299
00:23:07,840 --> 00:23:08,760
Don't talk nonsense.

300
00:23:08,760 --> 00:23:10,920
The police have ruled out the suspicion of homicide.

301
00:23:10,920 --> 00:23:11,680
Your son...

302
00:23:11,680 --> 00:23:13,480
What happened to my son?

303
00:23:13,480 --> 00:23:14,960
It wasn't a homicide.

304
00:23:14,960 --> 00:23:17,160
Did he jump down by himself?

305
00:23:17,160 --> 00:23:17,840
Yes.

306
00:23:17,840 --> 00:23:20,770
I think you still want to shirk your responsibility.

307
00:23:20,840 --> 00:23:22,760
Give my son back!

308
00:23:23,920 --> 00:23:24,980
What are you doing?

309
00:23:25,240 --> 00:23:26,280
What are you doing?

310
00:23:26,280 --> 00:23:27,480
Let go. Let them go.

311
00:23:27,480 --> 00:23:29,080
What are you doing?

312
00:23:29,080 --> 00:23:30,640
You think we have no backing, right?

313
00:23:30,640 --> 00:23:31,760
I'm telling you,

314
00:23:31,760 --> 00:23:33,920
ordinary people are not easy to bully.

315
00:23:33,920 --> 00:23:35,760
Give my son back!

316
00:23:36,600 --> 00:23:37,640
To be honest,

317
00:23:38,440 --> 00:23:39,400
I am also very remorseful

318
00:23:39,400 --> 00:23:40,240
and guilty.

319
00:23:41,000 --> 00:23:41,880
Rest assured.

320
00:23:42,280 --> 00:23:43,600
Give us some time

321
00:23:43,600 --> 00:23:44,880
and trust.

322
00:23:45,200 --> 00:23:48,200
We will definitely investigate this matter clearly.

323
00:23:50,560 --> 00:23:51,280
Here,

324
00:23:52,200 --> 00:23:53,680
on behalf of Qiongzhou University,

325
00:23:53,680 --> 00:23:55,340
I sincerely apologize to you.

326
00:23:58,000 --> 00:23:58,840
I'm sorry.

327
00:23:59,640 --> 00:24:00,680
I'm sorry.

328
00:24:01,680 --> 00:24:05,400
Apologizing won't bring my son back.

329
00:24:06,200 --> 00:24:08,080
There are still some of Li Weihao's belongings in his dorm room.

330
00:24:08,080 --> 00:24:09,760
If you want to take them back,

331
00:24:09,760 --> 00:24:10,890
I can take you there.

332
00:24:14,200 --> 00:24:14,840
I'm sorry.

333
00:24:17,320 --> 00:24:18,580
You should go back too.

334
00:24:31,360 --> 00:24:32,520
Mr. Du,

335
00:24:32,520 --> 00:24:33,400
are you okay?

336
00:24:34,640 --> 00:24:35,920
I'm fine.

337
00:24:35,920 --> 00:24:38,520
It's just that you haven't been back in so many years.

338
00:24:38,520 --> 00:24:39,720
And now that you are,

339
00:24:39,720 --> 00:24:41,520
you have to see a scene like this.

340
00:24:43,040 --> 00:24:44,400
I'm really sorry.

341
00:24:48,480 --> 00:24:49,640
Actually,

342
00:24:50,000 --> 00:24:51,960
Weihao is my patient.

343
00:24:52,880 --> 00:24:54,560
About seven years ago,

344
00:24:54,560 --> 00:24:57,520
I registered a Tree Hole account on Weibo.

345
00:24:57,520 --> 00:24:58,720
It was mainly used to share

346
00:24:58,720 --> 00:25:00,280
psychological knowledge.

347
00:25:01,520 --> 00:25:02,840
At that time,

348
00:25:02,840 --> 00:25:03,960
Weihao

349
00:25:03,960 --> 00:25:06,360
was the first person to leave me a message.

350
00:25:07,440 --> 00:25:08,640
Over the past five years,

351
00:25:08,640 --> 00:25:11,280
I have been recording what he told me,

352
00:25:11,280 --> 00:25:12,640
and I initially concluded

353
00:25:12,640 --> 00:25:14,640
that Weihao might have depression.

354
00:25:17,000 --> 00:25:17,840
You mean

355
00:25:17,840 --> 00:25:19,300
Li Weihao had depression?

356
00:25:21,400 --> 00:25:23,520
He had a tendency towards depression,

357
00:25:23,520 --> 00:25:26,000
but after years of psychological counseling,

358
00:25:26,000 --> 00:25:28,000
he no longer had suicidal thoughts.

359
00:25:28,240 --> 00:25:30,000
I also really want to know

360
00:25:30,000 --> 00:25:31,080
why this happened.

361
00:25:32,560 --> 00:25:35,320
If I had noticed something wrong with Weihao earlier,

362
00:25:35,320 --> 00:25:36,520
maybe all of this

363
00:25:36,520 --> 00:25:37,720
wouldn't have happened.

364
00:25:37,720 --> 00:25:39,960
I will ask for two more days of leave from the hospital in Beijing

365
00:25:39,960 --> 00:25:41,760
until this matter is cleared up.

366
00:25:41,800 --> 00:25:42,800
No problem.

367
00:25:42,800 --> 00:25:43,920
If you need anything,

368
00:25:43,920 --> 00:25:45,320
we will fully cooperate.

369
00:25:45,400 --> 00:25:47,080
If you are short-handed,

370
00:25:47,080 --> 00:25:48,480
I will find you a partner.

371
00:25:53,360 --> 00:25:55,320
It's probably a call about Weihao.

372
00:25:55,560 --> 00:25:57,080
We are right in the thick of it now.

373
00:25:57,080 --> 00:25:58,400
Do you want to avoid it?

374
00:25:58,400 --> 00:25:59,360
No.

375
00:25:59,360 --> 00:26:00,440
At this juncture,

376
00:26:00,440 --> 00:26:02,320
our school absolutely cannot hide.

377
00:26:02,320 --> 00:26:03,780
I'll take this call first.

378
00:26:11,800 --> 00:26:12,440
Hello.

379
00:26:12,800 --> 00:26:13,440
Go ahead.

380
00:26:31,280 --> 00:26:32,410
Alright, Guixiang.

381
00:26:32,720 --> 00:26:33,850
It's just a sticker.

382
00:26:34,480 --> 00:26:35,280
Leave it.

383
00:26:35,720 --> 00:26:37,160
It belongs to my son.

384
00:26:38,560 --> 00:26:40,560
I want to take it home.

385
00:26:55,800 --> 00:26:57,560
My condolences, Ma'am.

386
00:27:11,280 --> 00:27:12,320
Xiaochao.

387
00:27:13,280 --> 00:27:15,400
Can you tell me

388
00:27:15,920 --> 00:27:18,000
what exactly happened?

389
00:27:18,520 --> 00:27:19,760
You and Xiaohao

390
00:27:19,760 --> 00:27:21,120
have been good friends since childhood.

391
00:27:21,120 --> 00:27:23,360
You must know him well, right?

392
00:27:24,760 --> 00:27:26,440
Can you tell me

393
00:27:27,000 --> 00:27:28,880
what happened to him?

394
00:27:28,880 --> 00:27:30,800
Why would he do such a thing?

395
00:27:31,440 --> 00:27:33,760
Xiaochao, please tell me.

396
00:27:33,760 --> 00:27:35,720
Tell me.

397
00:27:36,800 --> 00:27:37,720
Tell me.

398
00:27:37,720 --> 00:27:39,640
Say something.

399
00:27:40,000 --> 00:27:41,520
You are his parents.

400
00:27:41,960 --> 00:27:43,280
If you don't know,

401
00:27:43,760 --> 00:27:44,800
how should I?

402
00:27:45,880 --> 00:27:46,520
But...

403
00:27:50,920 --> 00:27:51,520
Alright.

404
00:27:51,520 --> 00:27:52,800
Alright.

405
00:27:53,080 --> 00:27:54,200
Let's go.

406
00:27:54,800 --> 00:27:55,600
Let's go.

407
00:27:56,880 --> 00:27:57,760
Alright.

408
00:28:26,320 --> 00:28:27,120
Chao.

409
00:28:33,400 --> 00:28:35,080
Chao, are you okay?
